name: Classic_Mission_60-inch_Bookcase
description:
Place this classic Mission-style 60-inch bookcase in your home or office for stylish vertical storage space. At only 24 inches wide, this five-foot-tall bookcase can fit into almost any spare space, allowing you easy access to your books, magazines and folders. Four shelves provide you with enough space to comfortably house your collections.
